# api-endpoints

## Meeting Management Endpoints
Importance Score: 85

Key routes implementing domain-specific meeting management:

1. Signal Extraction Pipeline
```
/meetings/{meeting_id}/signals
/meetings/{meeting_id}/extract
```
- Processes meeting transcripts into categorized business signals
- Extracts decisions, action items, blockers and risks
- Maintains signal relationships and hierarchies

2. Meeting Bundle Processing 
```
/meetings/bundle/process
```
- Processes uploaded meeting bundles with signal extraction
- Performs contextual metadata enrichment
- Links related knowledge graph entities

